                "reference": {
                  "code": "J,NP/A,386,245,1982",
                  "field": {
                    "reference_type": "J",
                    "reference": {
                      "code": "NP/A",
                      "number": null,
                      "volume": "386",
                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "245",
                      "version": null,
                      "material_number": null
                    },
                    "date": 1982
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "Many new transitions",
                "were established only in gamma-gamma-coincidences.",
                "Intensities in these cases were estimated relative",
                "to the known strongest peaks in each gate using",
                "therelative efficiency scale from special Ra and 36C1",
                "measurements. In such way a several new primary",
                "transitions, namely 6424,6329,5892,5610,5482, 5371",
                "and 5089 keV which have been masked earlier by",
                "transitions in 124Te were observed."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": "R.Georgii+",
                "reference": {
                  "code": "J,NP/A,592,307,1995",
                  "field": {
                    "reference_type": "J",
                    "reference": {
                      "code": "NP/A",
                      "number": null,
                      "volume": "592",
                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "307",
                      "version": null,
                      "material_number": null
                    },
                    "date": 1995
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The energy calibration",
                "was made relative to the low and high-energy",
                "transitions in 124Te which contributed to the",
                "capture cross section in the target to about 70%."
              ]
            }
          ],
